OL,3,CUK sanctions Iranians accused of
OL,4,Cplanning attacks in Britain
OL,6,FThe UK has issued 12 new sanctions on
OL,7,Findividuals and groups accused of
OL,8,Fplanning attacks in the UK on behalf
OL,9,Fof Iran.
OL,11,FOn Monday, the Foreign Office imposed
OL,12,Ftravel bans and froze the assets of
OL,13,Fnine people for carrying out "hostile
OL,14,Factivity" in the UK and elsewhere.
OL,16,FAnother three sanctions were issued on
OL,17,Fentities, including the Zindashti
OL,18,FNetwork, who were sanctioned by the EU
OL,19,Flast year and said to be connected to
OL,20,FIran's Ministry of Intelligence and
OL,21,FSecurity.
OL,26,@uD@^OUvD@IO]
