OL,3,CUK sanctions Iranians accused of
OL,4,Cplanning attacks in Britain
OL,6,FThe Zindashti Network has "carried out
OL,7,Fnumerous acts of transnational
OL,8,Frepression" for the Iranian
OL,9,Fgovernment, including kidnappings and
OL,10,Fassassinations of critics of the
OL,11,Fregime, according to the EU.
OL,13,FAmong those sanctioned are five
OL,14,Fmembers of the Zarringhalam family `
OL,15,FFarhad, Fazlolah, Mansour, Nasser and
OL,16,FPouria ` who are said to have helped
OL,17,Ffinance efforts to "destabilise" the
OL,18,FUK.
OL,26,@nD@[OUpD@KO]yD@TOUyD@`O]
