OL,3,CUK sanctions Iranians accused of
OL,4,Cplanning attacks in Britain
OL,6,FMansour, Nasser and Fazlolah
OL,7,FZarringhalam were sanctioned by the US
OL,8,Flast year for their involvement in
OL,9,FIran's "shadow banking" network.
OL,11,FThe US Treasury said the trio had
OL,12,F"collectively laundered billions of
OL,13,Fdollars" for Iran through a network of
OL,14,Ffront companies in the UAE and Hong
OL,15,FKong.
OL,17,FCompanies linked to their network
OL,18,FBerelian Exchange and GCM Exchange,
OL,19,Fwere also sanctioned on Monday.
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@WO]tD@AOUuD@HO]
