OL,3,CUK sanctions Iranians accused of
OL,4,Cplanning attacks in Britain
OL,6,FOthers accused of "threatening,
OL,7,Fplanning or conducting attacks"
OL,8,Finclude Turkish national Ekrem Oztunc,
OL,9,FAzerbaijani national Namiq Salifov and
OL,10,FIranian national Nihat Abdul Kadir
OL,11,FAsan.
